msgid "When to refer to a specific Godot version"
msgstr "何時應標示 Godot 版本"

msgid ""
"Most of the time, the class reference and the manual should not specify the "
"first version in which a feature is added. This is because the documentation "
"describes the *current* features of the engine. Documentation will be read "
"and maintained for many versions after it is initially written, and a "
"reference to a first supported version is only relevant for a few versions "
"after a feature is added. After that, it becomes historical trivia best left "
"to a dedicated changelog."
msgstr ""
"大多數情況下，類別參考和手冊不應標示功能首次加入的版本。這是因為文件描述的是*"
"目前*的引擎功能。文件初版之後會跨多個版本被閱讀及維護，而首次支援版本的註明只"
"在新增後幾個版本內有用，之後便成為歷史資訊，建議留給變更日誌。"

msgid "Follow these guidelines for when to refer to a specific Godot version:"
msgstr "如需標示 Godot 版本，請遵循以下原則："

msgid ""
"If a feature was added in the current major version (4.x), **you can "
"specify** the feature is new in 4.x."
msgstr "若功能是當前主版（4.x）才加入， **可以標註** 此為 4.x 新功能。"

msgid ""
"If a feature or default approach to a problem was changed between major "
"versions (3.x -> 4.x), describe the current feature in the main body of the "
"page, and optionally add a brief sentence or note block to compare 3.x and "
"4.x."
msgstr ""
"若功能或解決方式在主版間（如 3.x → 4.x）變更，正文應敘述當前功能，另可簡述與"
"舊版比較。"

msgid ""
"If a large feature is added in a 4.x minor version, **you can specify** the "
"minor version when it was added. Large features have a whole page or large "
"section of documentation. In many cases it should still be avoided, since "
"it's only relevant for the next few minor versions."
msgstr ""
"若大型功能在 4.x 次版新增， **可以標示** 加入的次版號。通常這會佔據一整頁或大"
"章節，但大多數狀況下仍應避免，因為只對少數新舊版本有意義。"

msgid ""
"If a small feature is added in a 4.x minor version, **do not specify** the "
"minor version when it was added. Small features have only a short section of "
"documentation, or are minor additions to existing features."
msgstr ""
"若小型功能在 4.x 次版新增， **不須標示** 加入的次版號。這類功能通常只佔一小"
"節，或僅為現有功能的小增補。"

msgid ""
"If the default approach to a problem is changed in a 4.x minor version, **do "
"specify** the minor version in which a new default approach was added. For "
"example, the change from ``TileMap`` to ``TileMapLayer`` in 4.3."
msgstr ""
"若解決方式在 4.x 次版變更預設， **應標示** 變更的版本。例如 4.3 版將 "
"``TileMap`` 改為 ``TileMapLayer`` 。"

msgid ""
"If a feature was added in a 3.x major or minor version, **do not specify** "
"when the feature was added. These features are old enough that the exact "
"version in which they were added is not relevant."
msgstr ""
"功能若是在 3.x 版（主版或次版）新增， **不需標示** 加入版本，這類功能已太舊，"
"標示版號意義不大。"

